title: Your Teemoing shop
body:
How was everyone's Teemoing shop?

Me personally I was slightly disappointed as I haven't played 4 of the 6 champs in a game. And the other two I have played once or twice total.

But still cool to see that I get random discounts on some decent skins if I did play those champs.
So how was yours? leave a comment and vote below!

My vote is that it is ok, I mean the skins are awesome. it just seems weird to get skins for champs I don't play.
